high_descs: Turn left, go forward all the way, turn left to face the sink.
Take the knife at the edge of the counter.
Turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn right after passing the fridge to face the blue bin.
Cut the apple in the blue bin into pieces.
Stay at the bin.
Take a piece of apple from the bin.
Turn right, go forward, turn left to face the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave. Take the apple from the microwave.
Turn right to face the counter with the toaster.
Put the apple in front of and to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left to go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the blue trash can on the left of the refrigerator.
Cut the apple inside the trashcan
Place the knife in the trash can.
Pick up a piece of the cut apple.
Turn around to go back into the kitchen and go to the microwave.
Microwave the cut apple piece and take it out.
Turn right to face the counter with a toaster.
Place the microwaved piece of apple on the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved piece of apple by the toaster.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the corner of the counter, between the sink and the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter, in front of the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the door, making a right just after the refrigerator, and walk up to the blue bin to the left of the refrigerator.
Cut the apple, in the back of the blue bin, into slices.
Place the knife in the blue bin.
Pick up one of the apple slices from the blue bin.
Back up and turn right, back into the kitchen, then turn left at the microwave, past the refrigerator.
Place the apple slice in the microwave, heat it up, and remove the apple slice from the microwave.
Turn to the counter at your right, where the toaster is.
Place the apple slice on the counter, in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple slice on the counter.
